{"tid":1639921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［陰謀論］有冇諗過「蒙面法」係個高汁局？","createTime":"2019-10-08T18:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T19:13:10.000Z","uid":318952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"169b2696c42efd4d5825dc53ea304fe5c94d3e88","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:54:53.000Z","msg":"唔好急住少我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先蒙面法擺到明試水溫 <br />\n我哋就好似中咗降頭咁走去日日開花、裝修<br />\n但係諗深一層，我哋五理條法林奠點推下一條<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「網禁」</span></span><br />\n呢幾日真係證明一切<br />\n夜麻麻十一點上水站內有蒙面人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/109292827074154/videos/437609723555447/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F109292827074154%2Fvideos%2F437609723555447%2F&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=7ac2a6ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/109292827074154/videos/437609723555447/</a><br />\n港鐵站啲機用得照封？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/todayreview67/videos/2602665689753616/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftodayreview67%2Fvideos%2F2602665689753616%2F&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=5c7b4ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/todayreview67/videos/2602665689753616/</a><br />\n目的令一班中立撚、廢老、港豬因為封站同冇機而感唔耐煩 但隻死貓唔會係黨鐵食<br />\n其實林奠仲係度嫌你地唔夠勁。派鬼搞大件事<br />\n咁佢就可以順理成章用緊急法<br />\n到時班港豬就完全唔會覺得有乜問題<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n其實民意喺我哋度，班蝗蟲日日神助攻。<br />\n外國人都撐我地 我地點解要自打嘴巴<br />\n喺呢個時候我哋更加應該證明手足係和平的<br />\n呢個時候急嘅唔應該係我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火燒眼眉既係林奠！我地何必自亂陣腳？<br />\n對唔住！手足需回血<br />\n個人覺得日日口罩已足夠了<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"d7a4b8044390747ad05455a398ce05b197f744ad","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7c45e94a283558ec93e20d793f164ef895dd76a1","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:55:13.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b784b7f2784eb93027fbd6b1538848328ce097aa","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"求幫推,p仔冇力"},{"pid":"0c5613750bab665055daadb3326c2539033bb42b","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:55:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"612d93967090d80a91cee2e406711599fbdad60b","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"18fced6e7149ce7428dab00947c0a241c81d2de2","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:56:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"07f4513065a4a9be4bab27bdab28e0baae479d5b","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:56:44.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"433197a8919760e642eb17be3b6c4c4509b1bb3c","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:56:56.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d959dbdb9cca8468e8681d7a2ec7a36cef17c984","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f58cb5f99701768e7ff58b855a879f061b21fa00","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:57:18.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3b31e0fa527cbf0ff355c4414a823d1daaa9e47a","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:57:30.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"7570f499c053416e2182c570a46a0a8d47a70201","tid":1639921,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T18:58:01.000Z","msg":"推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/l